</ul>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="../../w/index-title=English-language_spelling_reform&action=edit&section=19.php.html" title="Edit section: References">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="References">References</span></h2>
<div class="reflist references-column-width" style="-moz-column-width: 30em; -webkit-column-width: 30em; column-width: 30em; list-style-type: decimal;">
<ol class="references">
<li id="cite_note-1"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-1">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.archive.org/details/handbooksimplif00boargoog"><i>Handbook of Simplified Spelling</i></a>. <a href="Simplified_Spelling_Board" title="Simplified Spelling Board">Simplified Spelling Board</a>, 1920. p.3</span></li>
<li id="cite_note-2"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-2">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><i>Handbook of Simplified Spelling</i>, p.4</span></li>
